### AI Roleplay Backend API 测试

### 1. 基本健康检查
GET http://localhost:18080/test

### 2. 简单聊天测试 (需要有效的API Key)
GET http://localhost:18080/api/chat/simple?message=你好&userId=test-user-001

### 3. POST方式聊天测试
POST http://localhost:18080/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好，我是新用户",
  "userId": "user-001"
}

### 4. 带角色的聊天测试
POST http://localhost:18080/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "介绍一下你自己",
  "userId": "user-001",
  "characterId": 1
}

### 5. 获取会话历史记录
GET http://localhost:18080/api/chat/history/user_user-001_general

### 6. 获取带角色的会话历史记录
GET http://localhost:18080/api/chat/history/user_user-001_char_1

### 7. 清除会话历史记录
DELETE http://localhost:18080/api/chat/history/user_user-001_general

### 8. 流式聊天测试 (需要有效的API Key)
POST http://localhost:18080/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "请用流式方式回答：什么是人工智能？",
  "userId": "user-002"
}
